The '''Great Siege''' was a conflict, recalled by [[Gorbag]] during the [[War of the Ring]] while talking to [[Shagrat]].<ref>{{TT|Choices}}, p. 739</ref> He was most likely referring to the [[Siege of Barad-dûr]] by the [[Last Alliance]],<ref>{{HM|RC}}, p. 500</ref> which lasted from {{SA|3434}}<ref>{{App|SA}}, entry for the year 3434</ref> until {{SA|3441|n}}.<ref>{{App|SA}}, entry for the year 3441</ref>

